    excerpt: "Assalamualaikum wa Rahmatullahi wa Barakatuhu The Hilal Council of Canada has received no confirmed sightings of the new moon. Thus, the first day of Ramadan will be Thursday. The first night of taraweeh will be Wednesday, February 18th, 2026. Isha salaah will be at 7:30 PM, and taraweeh salaah will begin shortly after. For more…",
    category: "Moonsighting",
    contentHtml: "\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Assalamualaikum wa Rahmatullahi wa Barakatuhu</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The Hilal Council of Canada has received no confirmed sightings of the new moon. <strong>Thus, the first day of Ramadan will be Thursday</strong>. The first night of taraweeh will be Wednesday, February 18th, 2026.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Isha salaah will be at 7:30 PM, and taraweeh salaah will begin shortly after.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">For more information on Hilal Council of Canada, please visit: <a href=\"http://www.hilalcouncilofcanada.com\">http://www.hilalcouncilofcanada.ca</a> or <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hilal_council?s=03\">https://twitter.com/hilal_council?s=03</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Management<br>Islamic Centre Of Markaham &#8211; Masjid Darul Iman<br><a href=\"https://daruliman.org/mystaging02\">www.daruliman.org</a></p>\n",
